WEBVTT

00:00.440 --> 00:04.838
Welcome to the heart of recreational excellence at the Student Activity and Recreation

00:04.886 --> 00:08.110
center, abbreviated SARC, where we are

00:08.142 --> 00:11.754
dedicated to enhancing learning and promoting healthy lifestyles.

00:12.654 --> 00:16.566
At the heart of our campus lies the open air amphitheater where students

00:16.630 --> 00:19.766
gather for performances, events and meetings under the

00:19.790 --> 00:23.398
open sky. As the hub of student activity,

00:23.566 --> 00:26.662
SARC serves the diverse needs of our student body and the

00:26.678 --> 00:30.904
wider university community, fostering teamwork, professionalism and

00:30.944 --> 00:34.920
enthusiasm while supporting student development adjacent

00:34.952 --> 00:38.256
to it. Casa Coffee restaurant Cafe provides

00:38.280 --> 00:42.104
a cozy atmosphere for students to unwind and socialize over a cup of their favorite

00:42.144 --> 00:45.920
brew or cake, but the culinary delights

00:45.992 --> 00:49.416
don't end there. Whether you're craving traditional indian

00:49.480 --> 00:53.692
flavors or international cuisine, our food court has you covered.

00:53.888 --> 00:57.492
Our food court boasts a variety of outlets including greenocks,

00:57.548 --> 01:01.196
the waffle truck, fat guys kitchen, koila kabob,

01:01.260 --> 01:05.292
baratheon and bur Grill. Offering something to tantalize every

01:05.348 --> 01:09.188
taste bud. Ample seating and an ambient atmosphere

01:09.236 --> 01:12.892
provides a soothing space to relax and unwind after a long

01:12.948 --> 01:13.544
day.

01:17.564 --> 01:21.534
Our multi purpose rooms cater to a variety of activities from

01:21.574 --> 01:25.454
workshops to club meetings, ensuring there's always something exciting

01:25.534 --> 01:29.694
happening on campus. For those seeking entertainment,

01:29.814 --> 01:32.702
our theater offers a space for movie screenings,

01:32.798 --> 01:35.594
performances and cultural events.

01:39.014 --> 01:42.590
Venture upstairs and you'll find our bowling alley a

01:42.622 --> 01:46.118
favorite spot for friendly competition and social gatherings.

01:46.286 --> 01:49.494
We have dedicated art and music rooms that provide creative

01:49.534 --> 01:52.484
outlets for expression and exploration.

01:52.984 --> 01:56.768
Further, our open terrace provides the perfect setting for sky

01:56.816 --> 02:01.016
watching and club activities under the night sky. At SARC,

02:01.120 --> 02:04.880
we are committed to creating a campus environment where every student can

02:04.912 --> 02:08.704
thrive, whether it's through our state of the art facilities or our vibrant

02:08.744 --> 02:09.624
programs and events.
